      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "关兴",
        "张苞"
      ],
      "text": "参见皇伯。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00008",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "贤侄出营与何人交战？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00009",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "关兴",
        "张苞"
      ],
      "text": "适才在营前骂阵，正遇吴将谭雄。是我二人，将他擒在马下，请皇伯发落。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00010",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "将谭雄押进帐来！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00011",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刀斧手押谭雄同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00012",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "大骂谭雄好大胆，擅敢领兵到阵前。人来与孤将他斩，人头号令在营前。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00013",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刀斧手押谭雄同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00014",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "呀，贤侄，今日初次出兵，就擒来仇人谭雄，真虎将也！内侍，看宴伺候，今当与二位皇侄贺功。老将军，你也来呀！",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00015",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "在大营排宴把酒饮，叫一声二贤侄细听分明：适才间营外来对阵，擒来了吴将显威名。理当分功把赏论，胜似蜀营众老臣！",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00016",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "听一言来怒气生，我主说话太欺情。酒席宴前把功论，分明笑我老无能。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00017",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "且住，向那关兴、张苞，乃是子侄之辈，阵前擒来谭雄，无非是些许一点功劳；我主隆恩，在酒席宴前，夸了又夸，奖了又奖，分明是笑我老将无用。也罢！我不免私自出营，去到阵前，匹马单刀，生擒潘璋，活捉吴侯。那时方显俺黄忠不老！",
      "text_length": 107
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00018",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "胸中妙计安排稳，去至阵前会敌人。怒气不息出大营，要学当年取定军。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00019",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄忠下。报子上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00020",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "报子"
      ],
      "text": "黄老将军，私自出营，叫阵去了！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00021",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "不好了！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00022",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "听一言来心内惊，营中气坏老将军。二贤侄快去将他赶，快快保护黄汉升。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00023",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关兴、张苞同下。刘备下。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00024",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四大铠、张嶷同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00025",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "张嶷"
      ],
      "text": "三国相争斗，将士用机谋。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00026",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "报子上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00027",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "报子"
      ],
      "text": "黄老将军到！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00028",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张嶷"
      ],
      "text": "有请。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00029",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "报子下，黄忠上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00030",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张嶷"
      ],
      "text": "呀，老将军！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00031",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "嘿！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00032",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张嶷"
      ],
      "text": "老将军到此何事？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00033",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "将军有所不知：只因关兴、张苞，在阵前擒得谭雄，无非是些小的功劳；我主隆恩，在酒席宴前，夸了又夸，奖了又奖，分明是笑我老将无用。是我忿气出营，要匹马单刀，去到阵前，活捉潘璋，生擒吴侯。那时方显我黄忠不老！",
      "text_length": 101
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00034",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张嶷"
      ],
      "text": "你本来的老了。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00035",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "将军呐！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00036",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "将军说话言蹊跷，不由黄忠怒心梢。你看我八十二岁老黄忠，哪些儿显老？",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00037",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张嶷"
      ],
      "text": "你实实的老了！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00038",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "呸！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00039",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "一言气坏将英豪。怒发冲冠出营道，两军阵前立功劳。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00040",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00041",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、潘璋同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00042",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "潘璋"
      ],
      "text": "吾，东吴大将潘璋。自从关公被害，吴侯将他的刀马赐与某家。那赤兔马，不吃草料而亡；这刀，到我手中，并未斩过上将。闻听黄忠，前来讨战，待我前去会他一会。众将官，起兵前往。",
      "text_length": 83
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00043",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00044",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "崔玉、史纪同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00045",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔玉",
        "史纪"
      ],
      "text": "吾，",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00046",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔玉"
      ],
      "text": "东吴大将崔玉，",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00047",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史纪"
      ],
      "text": "史纪。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00048",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔玉"
      ],
      "text": "请了。今有黄忠前来讨战，你我杀上前去。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00049",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄忠上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00050",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "来将通名受死！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00051",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔玉"
      ],
      "text": "崔玉。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00052",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "史纪"
      ],
      "text": "史纪。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00053",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "无名小卒，饶尔不死，去罢！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00054",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄忠下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00055",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔玉"
      ],
      "text": "你看黄忠老儿，未曾交锋，他竟自败下阵去，待我赶上！",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00056",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "崔玉、史纪同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00057",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄忠上，崔玉、史纪同上，黄忠下。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00058",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔玉"
      ],
      "text": "你看黄忠，虽然败阵，他马蹄不乱。待我赶上，定要死在他手。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00059",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "崔玉、史纪同下。黄忠上，崔玉、史纪同上。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00060",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔玉"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟，你与我压住阵脚，待我摘这个老倭瓜！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00061",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄忠杀崔玉、史纪。崔玉、史纪同下。潘璋上，对阵。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00062",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "来将通名！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00063",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "潘璋"
      ],
      "text": "大将潘……",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00064",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "“潘”什么？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00065",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "潘璋"
      ],
      "text": "潘璋！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00066",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "一见潘璋怒冲发，胆大奸贼敢会咱！催马提刀把仗打，少时叫尔染黄沙。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00067",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "潘璋"
      ],
      "text": "听一言来怒气发，黄忠老儿听根芽：本帅今日兴人马，老贼胆敢动杀法！",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00068",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄忠、潘璋起打，潘璋败下，黄忠下。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00069",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、马忠同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00070",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马忠"
      ],
      "text": "俺，马忠。奉了吴侯之命，攻打蜀兵。来，杀上前去。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00071",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄忠上，对四龙套。潘璋上，黄忠、潘璋同开打，潘璋下，黄忠下。马忠上，潘璋上。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00072",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马忠"
      ],
      "text": "元帅胜负如何？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00073",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "潘璋"
      ],
      "text": "黄忠老儿，杀法厉害，如何是好？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00074",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马忠"
      ],
      "text": "这有何难？待末将射他一箭。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00075",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "潘璋"
      ],
      "text": "好，埋伏了。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00076",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄忠上，马忠射，黄忠中箭，下。众人同下。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00077",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "那贼暗地把箭放，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00078",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄忠上，众人同上，开打，过河。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00079",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮紧板",
      "speakers": [
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "text": "倒叫老夫无主张。今日暗入天罗网，杀得老夫无躲藏。气力不佳难抵挡，",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00080",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关兴、张苞同上，救黄忠同下。龙套同下。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00081",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "潘璋"
      ],
      "text": "蜀将收兵，你我一同回营交令。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013011_e00082",
      "play_id": "01013011",
      "scene_id": "01013011_s07",
      "scene_no": 7,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}